  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases a stem of flowering sage, likely purple sage, with delicate purple and dark burgundy buds and blossoms. The flowers are tubular in shape and arranged along the stem in a vertical pattern. The buds are pointed and tightly closed, while some flowers are partially open, revealing a hint of their inner structure. The leaves are elongated, textured, and a darker shade of purple-green. A soft, blurred green background provides a natural backdrop, emphasizing the plant\u2019s colors and form. The lighting is soft and diffused, enhancing the texture and details of the sage.",
